N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21ยง 1.9 - Notification of change of address

State Regulations

Any applicant, prospective licensee, registrant, licensee, or
petitioner who changes his name or his residence address shall immediately
notify the commission in writing of such change. Notes
